 songs), rapping (five songs)\n*DJ Yella \u2013 sampling & drum programming (seven songs), rapping (one song)\n*The D.O.C. (guest) \u2013 rapping (one song)\n\n==Charts==\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n!Chart (1989)<ref name=AMG-Sales/><ref name=acharts/>\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US [[Billboard 200|''Billboard'' Top LPs]]<!-- chart name at time of charting -->\n| 37\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' [[Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums|Top Soul LPs]]\n| 9\n|-\n!Chart (1991)\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australian Albums ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref name=\"Australia\">{{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-albums-the-weeknd-takes-top-spot-on-australian-chart-20150905|title=ARIA Albums: The Weeknd Takes Top Spot On Australian Chart|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=September 5, 2015|accessdate=September 5, 2015}}</ref>\n| 51\n|-\n{{albumchart|New Zealand|43|artist=N.W.A|album=Straight Outta Compton|rowheader=true|accessdate=September 10, 2015}}\n|-\n!Chart (2003)<ref name=AMG-Sales/><ref name=acharts/>\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Irish Albums Chart\n| 20\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| UK Albums Chart\n| 35\n|-\n!Chart (2015\u201316)<ref name=\"hiphopdx.com\"/>\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Australian Albums ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.noise11.com/news/aria-albums-troye-sivan-wild-ep-debuts-at-no-1-20150912|title=ARIA Albums: Troye Sivan 'Wild' EP Debuts At No 1|publisher=Noise11|last=Ryan|first=Gavin|date=September 12, 2015|accessdate=September 12, 2015}}</ref>\n| 8\n|-\n{{albumchart|Austria|55|artist=N.W.A|album=Straight Outta Compton|rowheader=true|accessdate=September 10, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|France|17|artist=N.W.A|album=Straight Outta Compton|rowheader=true|accessdate=September 21, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Germany|36|artist=N.W.A|album=Straight Outta Compton|rowheader=true|accessdate=September 10, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Irelan