opranos]]'' (HBO)\n\n==Winners and nominees==\n\n===2000s===\n{| class=\"wikitable\" width=\"55%\" cellpadding=\"5\"\n|-\n!width=\"10%\"  | '''Year'''\n!width=\"40%\" | '''Winners and nominees'''\n!width=\"15%\"  | '''Network'''\n!width=\"1%\"  |'''{{Abbr|Ref.|Reference}}'''\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2000<br /><small>([[Producers Guild of America Awards 2000|12th]])</small>||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''''[[The West Wing]]'''''||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''[[NBC]]'''\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|-\n| ''[[ER (TV series)|ER]]'' || NBC\n|-\n| ''[[Law & Order]]'' || NBC\n|-\n| ''[[Oz (TV series)|Oz]]'' || [[HBO]]\n|-\n| ''[[The Practice]]'' || [[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]]\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2001<br /><small>([[Producers Guild of America Awards 2001|13th]])</small>||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''''[[The West Wing]]'''''||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''NBC'''\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|-\n| ''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]'' || [[CBS]]\n|-\n| ''[[Law & Order]]'' || NBC\n|-\n| ''[[Six Feet Under (TV series)|Six Feet Under]]'' || HBO\n|-\n| ''[[The Sopranos]]'' || HBO\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2002<br /><small>([[Producers Guild of America Awards 2002|14th]])</small>||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''''[[24 (TV series)|24]]'''''||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]'''\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\n|-\n| ''[[CSI: Crime Scene Investigation]]'' || CBS\n|-\n| ''[[Six Feet Under (TV series)|Six Feet Under]] || HBO\n|-\n| ''[[The Sopranos]]'' || HBO\n|-\n| ''[[The West Wing]]'' || NBC\n|-\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|2003<br /><small>([[Producers Guild of America Awards 2003|15th]])</small>||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''''[[Six Feet Under (TV series)|Six Feet Under]]'''''||style=\"background:#FAEB86;\" | '''HBO'''\n|rowspan=\"5\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\